   "source": [
    "###   Cross-Correlation vs. Convolution\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "G = h \\otimes F \\\\\n",
    "G(i,j) = \\sum_{u=-k}^{k} \\sum_{v=-k}^{k} h(u,v)F(i+u,j+v)\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "G = h \\ast F \\\\\n",
    "G(i,j) = \\sum_{u=-k}^{k} \\sum_{v=-k}^{k} h(u,v)F(i-u,j-v)\n",
    "$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "3c284010",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Finite Impulse Response Convolution\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "y(n) = \\sum_{k=0}^{M-1}h(k)x(n-k)\n",
    "$$"
   ]
  },
